296
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:13,810
Oh! There.

297
00:21:30,490 --> 00:21:32,490
Got it. There we go.

298
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:37,670
<font color="#ff00ff">[all]</font> "Stop spying on me, creeps."

299
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:38,960
Well, shit.

300
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:40,090
<font color="#ff00ff">[principal]</font> William Byers.

