00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:38,310
Will?

308
00:22:38,390 --> 00:22:40,520
Huh? <font color="#ff00ff">[mumbles]</font>

309
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:43,070
Yeah. Yeah, sorry.

