00:23:09,630 --> 00:23:10,630
Okay.

316
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:32,360
- Hey, buddy.
- Hey.

317
00:23:33,740 --> 00:23:34,830
Hey.

318
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,590
<font color="#ff00ff">[clatters]</font>

319
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:17,910
<font color="#ff00ff">[whirring]</font>

320
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,040
Sir Will, how are you?

321
00:24:22,120 --> 00:24:23,830
Mom. Pop.

322
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:26,540
Let's take a look,
see what's going on here.

323
00:24:26,630 --> 00:24:30,170
I see you shaved off a pound
since we saw you last.

324
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:33,010
Must be making room
for all that Halloween candy.

325
00:24:33,090 --> 00:24:34,220
What's your favorite candy?

326
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:36,850
Desert island candy,
if you had to pick one?

327
00:24:36,930 --> 00:24:38,390
- I don't know.
- Come on.

328
00:24:38,470 --> 00:24:40,390
