what would you pick?

329
00:24:40,470 --> 00:24:42,980
- I guess... Reese's Pieces.
- <font color="#ff00ff">[mouthing]</font> Reese's Pieces.

330
00:24:43,060 --> 00:24:45,810
Good call. Good call.

331
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:47,190
I'm more of a Mounds guy,

332
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:51,490
but I gotta say, peanut butter
and chocolate, come on, hard to beat that.

333
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:53,400
All right, tell me
what's going on with you.

334
00:24:53,490 --> 00:24:55,160
Tell me about this episode you had.

335
00:24:56,740 --> 00:25:01,660
<font color="#ff00ff">[Will]</font> Well, my friends were there
and then they just weren't,

336
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,410
and I was back there again.

337
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:05,290
In the Upside Down?

338
00:25:06,670 --> 00:25:08,420
All right, so what happened next?

339
00:25:08,500 --> 00:25:15,010
I heard this noise, and so I went outside,
and it was worse.

340
00:25:15,090 --> 00:25:16,340
How was it worse?

341
00:25:17,010 --> 00:25:18,300
There was this storm.

342
00:25:18,390 --> 00:25:19,470
<font color="#ff00ff">[thunder crashing]</font>

343
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:25,020
Okay. So how did you feel
when you saw the storm?

344
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,100
I felt...

345
00:25:27,150 --> 00:25:28,150
frozen.

346
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:34,320
- Heart racing?
- Just frozen.

347
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:37,410
Frozen, cold frozen? Frozen to the touch?

348
00:25:37,490 --> 00:25:40,490
No. Like how you feel when you're scared,

349
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:44,960
and you can't breathe or talk
or do anything.

350
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:49,040
I felt... felt this evil,
like it was looking at me.

351
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:52,800
It was evil?

352
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:56,090
Well... <font color="#ff00ff">[clears throat]</font>
What do you think the evil wanted?

353
00:25:56,170 --> 00:25:57,430
To kill.

354
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:59,220
<font color="#ff00ff">[whirring rapidly]</font>

355
00:25:59,300 --> 00:26:00,800
To kill you?

356
00:26:01,430 --> 00:26:02,430
Not me.

357
00:26:05,020 --> 00:26:06,310
Everyone else.

358
00:26:19,450 --> 00:26:21,370
<font color="#ff00ff">[Owens]</font> All right,
I'm gonna be honest with you.

359
00:26:21,450 --> 00:26:24,370
It's probably gonna get worse
before it gets better.

360
00:26:24,450 --> 00:26:28,160
Worse? He's already had
two episodes this month.

361
00:26:28,250 --> 00:26:30,790
He'll likely have more
before the month is out.

